data.description: Beautiful home in The Commons of Artesia! Prosper ISD! Home has an open floor plan, multiple dining areas, office with French doors, and guest room located on the first floor. Kitchen features wood cabinets, island with bar seating, granite counters, and a massive walk-in pantry, all open to the living area with stone fire place. Spacious primary bedroom has a gorgeous bath with garden tub and steam shower. Upstairs you have a large game room, with flex space and two spacious bedrooms. Upgrades include, hardwood floors through out the entire downstairs, decorative light fixtures, brand new carpet, new garage doors and front door, elegant mirrors in all bathrooms, and fresh landscaping! Let's not forget the large backyard with a covered patio. There are so many perks to living in this neighborhood. Pools, parks, fitness centers, jogging trails, etc. Not to mention, PGA Headquarters and new Omni Resort Hotel is just down the street!
